promptStructure.imagePayloadExample:
{
  "model": "qwen-image-plus",
  "input": {
    "prompt": "Scene 1 keyframe for \"Shelter\". Brief: A bear and a dog become unlikely friends after surviving a storm together. World style: Temperate rainforest, moss-covered stone, storm light, cedar roots Character anchor: Young brown bear cub Secondary anchor: Stray border collie mix Shared scene prompt: Extreme close-up of rain-soaked border collie fur trembling, dog backed into hollow cedar log interior, Pacific Northwest forest, pre-dawn grey light filtering through entrance, shallow depth of field on water droplets Lighting and palette: cinematic realism with coherent contrast, location-appropriate color, and continuity across the full short. Consistency rules: preserve the core visual identity, scale logic, defining forms, and recurring elements across shots; avoid random replacement, contradictory details, or continuity drift."
  },
  "parameters": {
    "size": "1280*720",
    "prompt_extend": false
  }
}

promptStructure.videoPayloadExample:
{
  "model": "wan2.6-i2v",
  "input": {
    "img_url": "<scene_keyframe_url>",
    "prompt": "Generate a 720p cinematic video clip for scene 1 of \"Shelter\". Start from the approved keyframe image and preserve its core visual elements and continuity. Shared scene prompt: Extreme close-up of rain-soaked border collie fur trembling, dog backed into hollow cedar log interior, Pacific Northwest forest, pre-dawn grey light filtering through entrance, shallow depth of field on water droplets Motion direction: preserve the action, framing, and continuity implied by the shared scene prompt with natural motion blur and coherent movement. Pacing direction: movement and camera timing should support a 15-second clip with clean entry and exit frames for concat. Native audio direction for shot 1: Heavy rain, wind through trees, distant thunder Keep sound realistic and synchronized to motion. Avoid voice-over, exact scripted dialogue requirements, dialogue subtitles, or unrelated effects. Safety constraints: stable forms, stable recurring elements, no sudden background swaps, no subtitle burn-in, and no unrelated intrusions."
  },
  "parameters": {
    "resolution": "720P",
    "prompt_extend": false,
    "watermark": false,
    "duration": 15
  }
}
